                "name": "Undying Loyalty",
                "ability_type": "Supernatural",
                "ability_type_abbrev": "Su",
                "text": "When destroyed, a forsaken foot soldier leaves behind a ghostly green apparition that stands in the same square in which it was destroyed for 24 hours. The apparition doesn\u2019t hinder movement through the square and cannot take actions, but the allies of the destroyed forsaken foot soldier treat the apparition as an ally for the purpose of flanking and using teamwork feats. If the forsaken foot soldier is destroyed with positive energy or holy water, this apparition does not appear."
